        <updateDate>2019-09-18T11:58:35Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Fire Police Fairness Act</b></p> <p>This bill includes additional firefighters within the definition of &quot;public safety officer&quot; for purposes of death, disability, and education benefits under the Public Safety Officers' Benefits Program.</p> <p>Specifically, it includes as a public safety officer a firefighter whose primary duty during an emergency response is to secure the scene or manage traffic.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
